content: Unfortunately opted for a refund pretty quickly after purchase. In the "about app" section, was really excited about the setlist option, that was the decider for the purchase. It doesn't state that the setlist feature is another separate purchase again, which for me was misleading. It states the setlist feature is part of this purchase, which it is not. Pretty disappointing.
replyContent: Hi Brendon, Sorry to hear about your disappointment. In fact KatanaMan Pro DOES have all of the functionality to use set lists, as standard .. to display setlists, use them to select songs/patches, automatic patch checking, highlight set breaks, etc. The set lists are simply text files, with a simple format, which you can create with a text editor

content: I had to many challenges trying to connect to my PC, so I gave up on that and gave this a go. It was easy to connect and navigate my way through, really glad I found this app because its given me access to everything the katana has to offer all on a phone or tablet. I would recomend this to everyone. Great Job to the devs! Thank you.

replyContent: KatanaMan Pro does not come with pre-configured patches, however there are heaps of free patches (TSL format) available for download, which you can easily use with the app.

content: I'm so glad I stumbled upon this app while reinstalling my spider app...I was not able to do deep editing on my PC because my current windows software is not compatible..this app works flawless w my Katana 50....Rock On \m/
